</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Bridges" /><category term="Kamo River" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking south at the Sanjo Ohashi bridge with rapeseed flowers (nanohana) growing in the river. 川に菜の花が咲く三条大橋を南方向。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2404_A7R09016.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2404_A7R09016.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kamogawa Evening・鴨川の夕方</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240415/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kamogawa Evening・鴨川の夕方" /><published>2024-04-15T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-04-15T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kamogawa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240415/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
