</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Kamo River" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[People chillin’ on the Kamo River after a warm sunny day. 暖かな晴天に恵まれ、「鴨チル」する人々。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2404_A7R08995.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2404_A7R08995.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Momiji・もみじ</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240414/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Momiji・もみじ" /><published>2024-04-14T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2024-04-14T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/momiji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240414/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
