</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Foliage" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The leaves on the maple trees are coming out now, along with those on the cherry trees. Our cherry blossom season is coming to an end, overtaken by a flurry of bright green. カエデの葉が出始め、桜の葉も。花見の季節は終わったけど、鮮やかな緑が咲き乱れます。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2404_A7R08981-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2404_A7R08981-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>